<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ACARA</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 2px auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #66bc69;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        .content ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .content ul li {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .content ul li strong {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 150px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #66bc69;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #66bc69;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for registering with us. We are excited to have you on board.</p>
            <p>Hallo <%= username %>
            </p>
            <p>Here are your login details:</p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>
                        Nama:
                    </strong>
                    <%= fullName %>
                </li>

                <li><strong>
                        Email:
                    </strong>
                    <%= email %>
                </li>
                
                <li><strong>
                        Tanggal Pendaftaran:
                    </strong>
                    <%= createdAt %>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <a href= "<%= activationLink %>" class="button" >Login</a>

            <p>
                Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.
            </p>
            <p>
                Terima kasih,
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                &copy; 2024 All rights reserved | ACARA
            </p>
        </div>
</body>

</html>